### Rule 61: Advanced Error Handling

**Error Classification:**
```typescript
enum ErrorType {
  TRANSIENT = 'transient',      // Retryable
  PERMANENT = 'permanent',      // Not retryable
  RATE_LIMIT = 'rate_limit',    // Rate limited
  VALIDATION = 'validation',    // Invalid input
}

function classifyError(error: Error): ErrorType {
  if (error.status === 429) return ErrorType.RATE_LIMIT;
  if (error.status >= 400 && error.status < 500) return ErrorType.VALIDATION;
  if (error.status >= 500) return ErrorType.TRANSIENT;
  return ErrorType.PERMANENT;
}
```

**Custom Retry Logic:**
